These people are one of the most feared human races in the world. They are
strong, powerful men living in the wildlands. Innohu are stout warriors
and mighty shamans. They lead a barbaric life, with their own beliefs and
ways of living. They hunt a lot and form large, powerful tribes that
protect their own territories. Most of the Innohu believe that a great
spirit unites them with nature. They also worship animal gods, or spirits. 
They are well known for their incredible stamina and strength. They have 
dark hair and red-brown skin. Innohu men are big in size, about 190 cm tall,
and weigh as much as 110 kgs. They have a lifespan of around 120 years.
